  "texts": [
    "GBM8 cells were grown in Neurobasal media (Gibco) with 7.5 ml L-glutamine, 10 ml B27 supplement, 2.5 ml N2 supplement, 1 mg heparin, 10 μg EGF, 10 μg FGF, and 2.5 ml anti-anti.",
    "GBM12, GBM75, GBM85 and GBM123 cells were provided by Dr. Jann Sarkaria (Mayo Clinic, Rochester, MN).",
    "GBM75 and GBM123 were cultured in FBS medium, GBM12 and GBM85 were cultured in stem cell medium as the instruction from the provider.",
    "All OBSCs were generated from P8 Sprague-Dawley rat pups.",
    "Dissected brains were mounted on a vibratome platform submerged in ice-cold brain slice media (BSM)."
  ],
